<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Allowing regions within countries eg states to indulge in diplomacy. Economic paradiplomacy relates to trade and investment- it has been institutionalized in Federal (USA, Canada, Belgium), Quasi Federal- Spain, and non-Federal (Japan). City Diplomacy is also a phenomenon where cities forge international partnership eg, Kyoto Varanasi</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Advantages-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Decentralized dimension to international debates</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Promotion of trade, tourism, cultural ties and even post conflict reconciliation</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Local political activism can get international support</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Region specific diplomacy</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Reasons for growth-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Globalization - Central govt by itself may not be will equipped</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">On several subjects related to trade, investment, FDI - smaller regions are better suited for diplomacy</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Given India's size</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Paradiplomacy in India</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Constitutional provisions</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">MEA initiatives to engage diplomats with states - States division</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Growing number of summits in state where international investors </span></span></li></ol>
